Hey @Alsond5, this error is probably due to some logic error in your recursive function. The fact that it throws in the 3rd iteration shows that the base case and the proof of base case verifies correctly, but there is a problem on the assertions about the proof of the first dynamic iteration (I mean the proof of first iteration that is not the base case). Try commenting out different assertion lines in your recursive method to find which one is not asserting correctly. This may help you find the actual reason of the error. I can help you more if you share the code. I hope this helps!
